title: Software Uninstaller
description: This is an Uninstaller that goes beyond Windows' own 'add-remove' feature. Revo creates a restore point, then searches the drive for additional entries (including the Registry). A VERY effective uninstaller. The program offers 4 uninstall options, each more thorogh than the last. It first allows the program`s own uninstaller to run (the program you wish to uninstall), then searches for additional junk files that were left behind during the initial installation and after its`removal.
